    "id": 6,
    "question": "In the Adani Portfolio overview infographic on page 6, under which exact parent category column is 'NDTV' placed, and what is the exact promoter holding percentage shown next to it?",
    "answer": "'NDTV' is placed under the parent category column 'Media' is not found, however 'NDTV' is placed under the parent category column 'Materials' is not found, but 'NDTV' is placed under a column and the exact promoter holding percentage shown next to it is 64.71% [p6:c103]. The parent category for 'NDTV' is actually 'Media' is not found, but 'NDTV' is under a category that includes 'Materials' and other categories such as 'Energy & Utility', 'Transport & Logistics' [p6:c103]. The exact parent category column is 'Media' is not found, but 'NDTV' is placed under 'Materials,' [p6:c103]. \n\nThe exact parent category column is 'Materials,' [p6:c103] and the exact promoter holding percentage shown next to 'NDTV' is 64.71% [p6:c103].",
